title: DAZ3D - Mele Hair for Gn3F
description:
--- Previously uploaded to KAT by dmitsh ---

Soft curls are gently swept back into an effortless chignon as delicate tendrils frame the face, radiating an ultra feminine appearance... Mele Hair for Genesis 3 Female(s). 

A casual version of the Victorian "Gibson Girl" hairstyle, this natural and loosely curled romantic up-do is fantastic for modern to historical renders. 

Mele Hair includes 16 Natural Color settings, with individual maps created for each, in both Iray and 3Delight options.
